airs in 1858-59. and from Lieut. Col. J.E. Johnston's Map of the Southern Boundary of Kansas in 1857. The Map of the Creek Country by Lieut. L. C. Woodruff, Topl. Engrs., in 1850-51.\" Described in LC Many nations. Cut and mounted on cloth. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:12.572Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-05", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-05"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2011590003/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd402/g4021/g4021e/ct003199.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd402/g4021/g4021e/ct003199.gif#h=150&w=198", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd402:g4021:g4021e:ct003199/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1018&w=1346", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd402:g4021:g4021e:ct003199/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=2037&w=2692"], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["indian territory", "indians of north america", "united states", "oklahoma"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2011590003", "sheet", "2015-12-28t17:54:45", "2025-06-07t04:43:13.100000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "geography and map division", "catalog"], "score": 24.45244, "shelf_id": "G4021.E1 1866 .U5", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["indian territory", "oklahoma", "maps", "indians of north america", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T16:03:11.898Z", "title": "Indian Territory, with part of the adjoining state of Kansas, &c", "type": ["cartographic"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2011590003/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/okhi/batch_okhi_jam_ver01/data/sn83025020/00202191186/1907112601/0829.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "im